🔥 cursor-free-vip | Python
🎯 Primary Use Case: To bypass the free trial limitations of the Cursor AI IDE by automatically resetting the machine ID, allowing users to access Pro features without payment.
✨ Key Features: • Resets Cursor AI MachineID • Bypasses higher token limit • Supports Windows, macOS, and Linux • Multi-language support (English, 简体中文, 繁體中文, Vietnamese)
📖 Summary: This repository provides a tool to reset the Cursor AI IDE's machine ID, effectively bypassing free trial limits and enabling access to Pro features. It supports Windows, macOS, and Linux operating systems and offers multi-language support. The tool is intended for educational purposes and encourages users to support the original Cursor AI project.
